      <title>Continuum Green 创始人计划为投资者退出提供 2 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/continuum-green-founders-eye-200-million-loan-for-investor-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度可再生能源公司 Continuum Green Energy Ltd. 的创始人已聘请德意志银行筹集 2 亿美元贷款，为从其大股东手中购买股份提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/continuum-green-founders-eye-200-million-loan-for-investor-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:48:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
