      <title>中国人民银行加大力度反对长期国债反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/pboc-steps-up-rhetoric-against-long-end-government-bond-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行加大了对长期政府债券上涨的口头抵制力度，警告可能出现逆转，并暗示市场价格与经济前景之间的不匹配将得到纠正。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/pboc-steps-up-rhetoric-against-long-end-government-bond-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券牛市推动中国信贷收益率跌至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-credit-yields-drop-to-record-lows-on-bond-bull-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者在流动性充沛的金融体系中大量购买公司债券以提高回报，中国的本地信贷收益率已跌至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-credit-yields-drop-to-record-lows-on-bond-bull-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
